Package com.guidewire.util.webservices

Interface Summary
DataAPIShell.ShellAPI  
GWRemotable For internal use only
Classes that implement this interface can be serialized over SOAP.
GWSOAPOperation Deprecated. Use APILocator.getAuthenticatedProxy(Class, String, String, String)
GWSOAPProvider Deprecated. Use APILocator.getAuthenticatedProxy(Class, String, String, String)
SOAPAuthenticatedProxy Internal interface implemented by SOAP proxy returned from APILocator.getAuthenticatedProxy(Class, String, String, String).
 

Class Summary
APILocator APILocator is a utility class that simplifies getting a handle to, and authenticating with, a remote SOAP API [web-service] published by a Guidewire server.
CmdLineToolBase CmdLineTooBase will automatically parse server URL, username, password from command line, and will log in and log out before and after an API call.
CmdOptionBuilder A class to serve as an anti-corruption layer to build the command line options
DataAPIShell  
Globals Contains constant values used throughout the SOAP API implementation.
GWAxisSOAPPluginServlet GWServiceAxisServlet
GWEnumeration The base class for all SOAP enumerations defined in Java.
RemoteLogin Internal class used by APILocator's authentication handler.
SOAPClientConfigProvider Internal class used to read the gw-client-config.wsdd file.
SOAPOutboundHandler Internal class used to handle outbound SOAP requests.
ThreadSafeProxy Internal class that creates a thread safe wrapper around a potentially non-thread safe class by maintaining a pool of such classes and allocating an instance of the class per method call.
 

Exception Summary
RemoteLoginException Exception thrown with login fails.
